        <p id="maelz" style="font-size: smaller;"><i>âš  click above to get the file.... In the bot click "START"</i>
        </p>

        <div class="dstweb tweb">
            <a id="dstweb" href="#" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">OPEN IN TELEGRAM WEB</a>
            <p id="ds_par" style="font-size: smaller;"><i>âš  click above if the first link don't work</i> </p>
        </div>
